data.description: Beautiful mid-century home (with many upgrades) located in an established neighborhood.  This 3BD/2 Bath is move in ready.  This home sports a large lot with incredible mature landscaping.  There is plenty of space for your vehicles/RV and toys.  The front of the home has access from the city street and access to the back of the home from a platted city street.  Right outside the backdoor you will have a secluded city park with lots of trees and open space.  The inside has gorgeious archways and other unique features.  This home has a lot of built in storage space throughout.  The garage is single but and has three secure storage spaces on the outside of the garage.  The home also has a beautiful back deck/patio with a standalone brick BBQ fireplace.
